sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant GW as Recommendation Gateway
    participant ML as ML Recommendation Service
    participant FB as Fallback Engine
    participant LOG as Logs / Metrics

    U->>FE: Opens recommendations
    FE->>GW: GET /recommendations?trip_id=...
    GW->>ML: Request recommendations, timeout 3s

    alt ML healthy and confidence is high
        ML-->>GW: Recommendations + confidence
        GW->>LOG: mode=ml, response_time, confidence
        GW-->>FE: Unified recommendations response
    else ML unavailable or timeout or low confidence
        GW->>FB: Build fallback recommendations
        FB-->>GW: Ranked fallback candidates
        GW->>LOG: mode=fallback, reason, timings
        GW-->>FE: Unified recommendations response
    end

    FE-->>U: Shows recommendations
